---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Callout from '../../components/Callout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Maine Cannabis Official Resources" 
  description="Complete curated directory of official Maine cannabis resources. OCP portals, municipal contacts, state agencies, and regulatory bodies — all in one place."
  heroImage="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1589829545856-d10d557cf95f?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=1200&h=400"
>
  <article class="resource-hub">
    <div class="hub-header">
      <h1>Maine Cannabis Official Resources</h1>
      <p class="lead">The authoritative curated directory for Maine cannabis entrepreneurs. Every official state agency, municipal contact, licensing portal, and regulatory body — organized and linkable.</p>
    </div>

    <section>
    <h2>Bookmark This Page</h2>
    <Callout title="Most comprehensive Maine cannabis resource directory on the internet." type="passion">
      Journalists, attorneys, and business advisors use it. <strong>Last verified: April 2026.</strong>
    </Callout>
    </section>

    <div class="resource-sections">

      <section class="resource-section" id="state-agencies">
        <div class="section-header">
          <span class="section-icon">🏛️</span>
          <h2>State Agencies</h2>
        </div>
        <p>Primary regulatory bodies overseeing Maine's cannabis industry.</p>
        <div class="resource-grid">
          <div class="resource-card">
            <h3>Office of Cannabis Policy (OCP)</h3>
            <p>The primary regulatory agency for both medical and adult-use cannabis in Maine.</p>
            <ul class="resource-links">
              <li><a href="https://www.maine.gov/dafs/ocp/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">OCP Homepage</a></li>
              <li><a href="https://www.maine.gov/dafs/ocp/adult-use" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Adult-Use Program</a></li>
              <li><a href="https://www.maine.gov/dafs/ocp/adult-use/applications-forms" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Applications & Forms</a></li>
              <li><a href="https://www.maine.gov/dafs/ocp/adult-use/applications-forms" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">License Application Portal</a></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="resource-card">
            <h3>Maine Revenue Services</h3>
            <p>Handles cannabis tax collection including the 10% excise tax and 5.5% sales tax.</p>
            <ul class="resource-links">
              <li><a href="https://www.maine.gov/revenue/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Maine Revenue Services</a></li>
              <li><a href="https://www.maine.gov/revenue/tax-information" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Tax Information Portal</a></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="resource-card">
            <h3>Maine Department of Agriculture</h3>
            <p>Oversees cultivation licensing, hemp program, and agricultural compliance.</p>
            <ul class="resource-links">
              <li><a href="https://www.maine.gov/agriculture/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Department of Agriculture</a></li>
              <li><a href="https://www.maine.gov/agriculture/plants-indoor-hemp" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Hemp & Cultivation</a></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="resource-card">
            <h3>Maine CDC (Public Health)</h3>
            <p>Oversees the Medical Use of Cannabis Program and patient registry.</p>
            <ul class="resource-links">
              <li><a href="https://www.maine.gov/dhhs/mecdc/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Maine CDC</a></li>
              <li><a href="https://www.maine.gov/dhhs/mecdc/population-health/mmc/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Medical Cannabis Program</a></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="resource-card">
            <h3>Maine State Police</h3>
            <p>Handles background checks, seed-to-sale tracking (Metrc), and regulatory inspections.</p>
            <ul class="resource-links">
              <li><a href="https://www.maine.gov/dps/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Department of Public Safety</a></li>
              <li><a href="https://www.maine.gov/dps/msp/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Maine State Police</a></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="resource-card">
            <h3>Maine Secretary of State</h3>
            <p>Business entity registration, assumed names, and corporate filings.</p>
            <ul class="resource-links">
              <li><a href="https://www.maine.gov/sos/scorp/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Corporate Filings Portal</a></li>
              <li><a href="https://www.maine.gov/sos/scorp/services.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Business Services</a></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="resource-section" id="municipal-opt-in">
        <div class="section-header">
          <span class="section-icon">🗳️</span>
          <h2>Municipal Opt-In Directory</h2>
        </div>
        <p>Maine municipalities that have voted to allow adult-use cannabis businesses. You can only open a dispensary in an opt-in town. <a href="/guides/maine-dispensary-locations/">View our full municipal guide →</a></p>
        <div class="resource-grid">
          <div class="resource-card">
            <h3>Open Markets (Opt-In)</h3>
            <p>Towns that have formally opted into allowing adult-use cannabis retail operations.</p>
            <ul class="resource-links">
              <li><a href="https://www.portlandmaine.gov/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Portland</a> — $5,000 annual local fee</li>
              <li><a href="https://www.bangormaine.gov/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Bangor</a></li>
              <li><a href="https://www.lewistonmaine.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Lewiston</a></li>
              <li><a href="https://www.southportland.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">South Portland</a></li>
              <li><a href="https://www.auburnmaine.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Auburn</a></li>
              <li><a href="https://www.biddefordmaine.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Biddeford</a></li>
              <li><a href="https://www.brunswickmaine.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Brunswick</a> — $2,500 annual fee</li>
              <li><a href="https://www.mainebiddeford.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Biddeford</a></li>
              <li><a href="https://www.augustamaine.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Augusta</a></li>
              <li><a href="https://www.sanfordmaine.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Sanford</a></li>
              <li><a href="https://www.watervillelaughlin.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Waterville</a></li>
              <li><a href="https://www.obbme.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Old Orchard Beach</a></li>
              <li><a href="https://www.kennebunkmaine.us/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Kennebunk</a></li>
              <li><a href="https://www.scarborough.me.us/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Scarborough</a> — ❌ Not permitted</li>
              <li><a href="https://www.westbrookmaine.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Westbrook</a> — ❌ Delivery only</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="resource-card">
            <h3>Municipal Cannabis Contacts</h3>
            <p>Direct contacts for municipal clerks and planning offices in opt-in communities.</p>
            <ul class="resource-links">
              <li><a href="https://www.maine.gov/memap/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Maine Municipal Association</a></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="resource-section" id="business-services">
        <div class="section-header">
          <span class="section-icon">📋</span>
          <h2>Business Formation & Licensing</h2>
        </div>
        <p>Essential steps for registering your cannabis business entity in Maine.</p>
        <div class="resource-grid">
          <div class="resource-card">
            <h3>Business Registration</h3>
            <ul class="resource-links">
              <li><a href="https://www.maine.gov/sos/scorp/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Secretary of State Corporate Portal</a></li>
              <li><a href="https://www.maine.gov/sos/scorp/services.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Register a Maine LLC or Corporation</a></li>
              <li><a href="https://www.maine.gov/revenue/taxes/business-taxes" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Maine Business Tax Registration</a></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="resource-card">
            <h3>OCP Licensing</h3>
            <ul class="resource-links">
              <li><a href="https://www.maine.gov/dafs/ocp/adult-use/applications-forms" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Adult-Use License Applications</a></li>
              <li><a href="https://www.maine.gov/dafs/ocp/adult-use/application-process" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">License Application Process Guide</a></li>
              <li><a href="https://www.maine.gov/dafs/ocp/rules/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">OCP Rules & Statutes</a></li>
              <li><a href="https://www.maine.gov/dafs/ocp/resources/guidance" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">OCP Guidance Documents</a></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="resource-card">
            <h3>Background Checks</h3>
            <ul class="resource-links">
              <li><a href="https://www.maine.gov/dps/msp/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Maine State Police Background Checks</a></li>
              <li><a href="https://www.maine.gov/sos/scorp/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Criminal History Check (CHSE)</a></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="resource-card">
            <h3>Metrc Seed-to-Sale Tracking</h3>
            <ul class="resource-links">
              <li><a href="https://www.metrc.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Metrc — Cannabis Tracking System</a></li>
              <li><a href="https://www.maine.gov/dafs/ocp/adult-use" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">OCP Metrc Information</a></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="resource-section" id="taxation">
        <div class="section-header">
          <span class="section-icon">💰</span>
          <h2>Taxation & Banking</h2>
        </div>
        <p>IRS Section 280E, state taxes, and cannabis-friendly banking in Maine.</p>
        <div class="resource-grid">
          <div class="resource-card">
            <h3>Maine Cannabis Taxes</h3>
            <ul class="resource-links">
              <li><a href="https://www.maine.gov/revenue/taxes/sales-tax" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Maine Sales Tax Information</a></li>
              <li><a href="https://www.maine.gov/dafs/ocp/resources" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">OCP Tax Resources</a></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="resource-card">
            <h3>IRS 280E Guidance</h3>
            <p>Federal tax treatment of cannabis businesses. Due to Schedule I classification, standard business deductions are disallowed.</p>
            <ul class="resource-links">
              <li><a href="https://www.irs.gov/priorities/working-together-to-create-an-inclusive-tax-system" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">IRS Cannabis Tax Guidance</a></li>
              <li><a href="/guides/maine-cannabis-taxation-280e/">Our 280E Tax Guide →</a></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="resource-card">
            <h3>Cannabis Banking</h3>
            <p>Due to federal prohibition, cannabis businesses face banking access challenges.</p>
            <ul class="resource-links">
              <li><a href="https://www.maine.gov/dafs/ocp/resources/banking" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">OCP Banking Resources</a></li>
              <li><a href="https://www.cannasos.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Cannasos — Cannabis Banking Directory</a></li>
              <li><a href="/guides/maine-cannabis-banking-solutions/">Our Banking Guide →</a></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="resource-section" id="lab-testing">
        <div class="section-header">
          <span class="section-icon">🔬</span>
          <h2>Laboratory Testing</h2>
        </div>
        <p>Maine requires all cannabis products to be tested by OCP-certified laboratories.</p>
        <div class="resource-grid">
          <div class="resource-card">
            <h3>OCP-Approved Testing Labs</h3>
            <ul class="resource-links">
              <li><a href="https://www.maine.gov/dafs/ocp/resources" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">OCP Laboratory Resources</a></li>
              <li><a href="https://www.maine.gov/dafs/ocp/adult-use" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">OCP Testing Requirements</a></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="resource-card">
            <h3>Testing Standards</h3>
            <ul class="resource-links">
              <li><a href="https://www.maine.gov/dafs/ocp/rules/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">OCP Testing Lab Rules (Chapter 5)</a></li>
              <li><a href="/guides/maine-cannabis-product-testing-guide/">Our Testing Guide →</a></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="resource-section" id="security">
        <div class="section-header">
          <span class="section-icon">🔒</span>
          <h2>Security & Compliance</h2>
        </div>
        <p>OCP-mandated security requirements for dispensaries and cultivation facilities.</p>
        <div class="resource-grid">
          <div class="resource-card">
            <h3>OCP Security Requirements</h3>
            <ul class="resource-links">
              <li><a href="https://www.maine.gov/dafs/ocp/rules/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">OCP Security Rules</a></li>
              <li><a href="https://www.maine.gov/dafs/ocp/adult-use" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">OCP Security Plan Requirements</a></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="resource-card">
            <h3>Surveillance & Alarms</h3>
            <ul class="resource-links">
              <li><a href="https://www.maine.gov/dps/safe/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Maine alarm &amp; security resources</a></li>
              <li><a href="/guides/maine-dispensary-security/">Our Security Guide →</a></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="resource-section" id="legal">
        <div class="section-header">
          <span class="section-icon">⚖️</span>
          <h2>Legal Resources</h2>
        </div>
        <p>State bar association, legal aid, and cannabis-specific legal resources.</p>
        <div class="resource-grid">
          <div class="resource-card">
            <h3>Maine Bar & Courts</h3>
            <ul class="resource-links">
              <li><a href="https://www.courts.maine.gov/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Maine Judicial Branch</a></li>
              <li><a href="https://www.mainebar.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Maine State Bar Association</a></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="resource-card">
            <h3>Cannabis Law</h3>
            <ul class="resource-links">
              <li><a href="https://www.mainebiz.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">MaineBiz — Cannabis Business Coverage</a></li>
              <li><a href="https://www.maine.gov/dafs/ocp/rules/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">28-B M.R.S. (Cannabis Statutes)</a></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="resource-section" id="employment">
        <div class="section-header">
          <span class="section-icon">👷</span>
          <h2>Employment & Labor</h2>
        </div>
        <p>Maine labor laws, workers compensation, and workforce resources for cannabis businesses.</p>
        <div class="resource-grid">
          <div class="resource-card">
            <h3>Maine Department of Labor</h3>
            <ul class="resource-links">
              <li><a href="https://www.maine.gov/labor/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Maine DOL Homepage</a></li>
              <li><a href="https://www.maine.gov/labor/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Maine Department of Labor</a> — Workers compensation info</li>
              <li><a href="https://www.maine.gov/labor/laws_rules/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Maine Labor Laws</a></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="resource-card">
            <h3>Workforce Development</h3>
            <ul class="resource-links">
              <li><a href="https://www.mainecareers.maine.gov/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Maine Career Centers</a></li>
              <li><a href="https://www.maine.gov/decd/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Maine DECD</a> — SBDC and small business development</li>
              <li><a href="/guides/maine-dispensary-hiring/">Our Hiring Guide →</a></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="resource-section" id="industry">
        <div class="section-header">
          <span class="section-icon">🌐</span>
          <h2>Industry Associations & Media</h2>
        </div>
        <p>Cannabis industry organizations and publications covering the Maine market.</p>
        <div class="resource-grid">
          <div class="resource-card">
            <h3>National Industry</h3>
            <ul class="resource-links">
              <li><a href="https://www.cannabisbusinesstimes.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Cannabis Business Times</a></li>
              <li><a href="https://mjbizdaily.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Marijuana Business Daily</a></li>
              <li><a href="https://www.ganjapreneur.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Ganjapreneur</a></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="resource-card">
            <h3>Maine & New England</h3>
            <ul class="resource-links">
              <li><a href="https://www.mainebiz.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">MaineBiz — Cannabis Coverage</a></li>
              <li><a href="https://mainebeacon.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Maine Beacon</a></li>
              <li><a href="https://www.mainepublic.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Maine Public (NPR)</a></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

    </div>

    <Callout title="Need a Custom Referral?" type="info">
      If you need help finding the right professional for your specific situation — a cannabis attorney, CPA, real estate broker, or security provider — <a href="/directory/">visit our Verified Professional Directory</a>.
    </Callout>
  </article>
</Layout>

<style>
  .resource-hub { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; }
  
  .hub-header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 3rem; }
  .hub-header h1 { font-size: 2.5rem; color: var(--color-primary); margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .lead { font-size: 1.2rem; color: var(--color-text-light); max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; line-height: 1.7; }
  
  .resource-sections { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 4rem; margin-top: 3rem; }
  
  .resource-section h2 { font-family: var(--font-serif); color: var(--color-primary); font-size: 1.75rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .section-header { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .section-icon { font-size: 2rem; }
  .resource-section > p { color: var(--color-text-light); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; line-height: 1.6; }
  .resource-section > p a { color: var(--color-accent); font-weight: 600; }
  
  .resource-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr)); gap: 1.5rem; }
  .resource-card { background: var(--color-surface); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: 1.5rem; padding: 1.5rem; }
  .resource-card h3 { font-family: var(--font-serif); color: var(--color-primary); font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
  .resource-card > p { font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--color-text-light); margin-bottom: 1rem; line-height: 1.5; }
  
  .resource-links { list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0; }
  .resource-links li { margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .resource-links a { color: var(--color-accent); text-decoration: none; font-weight: 500; font-size: 0.9rem; }
  .resource-links a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
</style>
</Layout>
